4 SYNOPSIS:
5 Under existing law, the Alabama Board of
6 Cosmetology and Barbering is responsible for licensing
7 and regulating cosmetologists, barbers, estheticians,
8 manicurists, and other practitioners of beauty culture.
9 This bill would provide for the licensing and
10 regulation of makeup artists and the permitting of
11 lash/brow artists by the board.
12 This bill would provide for certain exemptions
13 and would authorize the operation of mobile studios.
14 This bill would also specify qualifications for
15 licensing and would provide qualifications for
16 grandfathering.
